name: SARS-COV-2ß-2
description:
My wallet has been infected by SARS-CoV-2ß, the virus responsible for COVID-19.

It was transmitted by bayneko (tz1ML9AAxDYsnoTKdS7NaF8TG3FGALTCVfFT) as a symbol of the invasive and ubiquitous nature of the virus and its psychological effects. A total of 96,186 viral copies have been sent to as many wallets.

First I thought it wouldn't affect me, but I was wrong.

Now the virus has mutated and I will probably infect many more people despite the sanitary precautions I have taken.

I am deeply sorry for this.
